text: Henri Kontinen and Andreas Siljeström were the defending champions, but they did not compete that year. Ken Skupski and Neal Skupski won the title, defeating Norbert Gombos and Adam Pavlásek in the final, 6–3, 7–6(7–3). ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw Slovak Open - Doubles 2014 Doubles
